response.original_title: Classic Television: Blooper Bonanza 1960's (featuring Laugh-In, McHale's Navy, Star Trek)
response.overview: Put on your bellbottoms, get out your freak flag and set your phasers to fun with this hilarious collection of bloopers from the groovy days of TV. From the hilarious hippie happenings of Laugh-In to the Sci-Fi screwups of TV's favorite five year mission, these comedic blunders, bumbles, and bloopers highlight the humiliating human foibles of the swinging 60s superstars. Featuring pop culture icons Goldie Hawn, William Shatner, Don Rickles, Tim Conway, Orson Wells, Sammy Davis , Jr. and more!
